>\n除左睇戲、食飯、散步，仲可以有咩做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最重要個樣你冇講</blockquote><br />\n我講緊剛剛拍拖無耐（未扑，唔打算扑）嘅情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98c3beff951379743994e5c38b1f50e43f976c7","tid":92032,"uid":2128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:45:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>A0<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打仲細咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊度細 19啦"},{"pid":"0646b8d0975b4ecda30899ef0d12cbe3c4278795","tid":92032,"uid":76945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A3，覺得拍拖好浪費時間，又要估條女諗乜、逗佢開心、比錢佢、傾計<br />\n一開始追到個下咪HAPPY，3個月已經乜都做過哂，好悶<br />\n寧願自己一個，自己想做咩就做咩，好自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果溝條女只係想扑野，我會選擇叫雞或者招SP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都差不多係咁（除左扑野呢part<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）覺得自由最好玩 要下下顧住對方好煩"},{"pid":"b998e759763de22fbf60de67415266b45acf793d","tid":92032,"uid":35957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:47:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>BTW 好想問下大家，究竟拍拖會去邊到？<br />\n除左睇戲、食飯、散步，仲可以有咩做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最重要個樣你冇講</blockquote><br />\n我講緊剛剛拍拖無耐（未扑，唔打算扑）嘅情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家成年人，扑野(做愛)係正常行為，無話時間耐唔耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通你條女要你縮沙咩"},{"pid":"d1f001ad4e73285a62a8cdeabd94bad5fb7f51b5","tid":92032,"uid":76945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>A0<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打仲細咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊度細 19啦</blockquote><br />\n19都唔大啊，有冇主動追下女仔先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c666e9200a762ca25fa22eebd0f9cc87a3ef83d","tid":92032,"uid":76945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:49:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>BTW 好想問下大家，究竟拍拖會去邊到？<br />\n除左睇戲、食飯、散步，仲可以有咩做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最重要個樣你冇講</blockquote><br />\n我講緊剛剛拍拖無耐（未扑，唔打算扑）嘅情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家成年人，扑野(做愛)係正常行為，無話時間耐唔耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通你條女要你縮沙咩</blockquote><br />\n試過女朋友主動要？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> BTW 認同係正常行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8c32637799916ba2cdf76e1b5eaf5bdd25bb39","tid":92032,"uid":42728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:49:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BTW 好想問下大家，究竟拍拖會去邊到？<br />\n除左睇戲、食飯、散步，仲可以有咩做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我真係同你一樣<br />\n除左扑野，真係諗唔到有咩好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最多咪一齊打下機，但都係打一陣姐<br />\n過左頭幾個月，了解多左，仲邊得黎咁多野傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4a9c9585fb3c42d955964f72d1ef7f3072b93c","tid":92032,"uid":76945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:53:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>BTW 好想問下大家，究竟拍拖會去邊到？<br />\n除左睇戲、食飯、散步，仲可以有咩做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我真係同你一樣<br />\n除左扑野，真係諗唔到有咩好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最多咪一齊打下機，但都係打一陣姐<br />\n過左頭幾個月，了解多左，仲邊得黎咁多野傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會真係諗唔到做咩，大家平時做開嘅野都唔同，出街真係會悶，屋企又會有屋企人，冇得話返屋企睇下劇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a488086b0bc67f4dde1d3ea7286015effc8828","tid":92032,"uid":14750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:53:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A3，覺得拍拖好浪費時間，又要估條女諗乜、逗佢開心、比錢佢、傾計<br />\n一開始追到個下咪HAPPY，3個月已經乜都做過哂，好悶<br />\n寧願自己一個，自己想做咩就做咩，好自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果溝條女只係想扑野，我會選擇叫雞或者招SP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同你一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbetween 你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e036d8146514034f66a6567252bdce2279f4fa1","tid":92032,"uid":36019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:54:22.000Z","msg":"就快比佢摙撚死"},{"pid":"f59531bf6e33e969f9d39a3e91fd4616dad46117","tid":92032,"uid":2128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:55:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n巴打仲細咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊度細 19啦</blockquote><br />\n19都唔大啊，有冇主動追下女仔先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br /