<blockquote><br />\n巴打仲細咋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊度細 19啦</blockquote><br />\n19都唔大啊，有冇主動追下女仔先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有曖昧過<br />\n次次都錯timing<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔把握就比人搶走咗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但曖昧過好過冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f098ed01a561f1cd8168d80f3c2980a027a80d","tid":92032,"uid":35957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T09:59:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>A3，覺得拍拖好浪費時間，又要估條女諗乜、逗佢開心、比錢佢、傾計<br />\n一開始追到個下咪HAPPY，3個月已經乜都做過哂，好悶<br />\n寧願自己一個，自己想做咩就做咩，好自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果溝條女只係想扑野，我會選擇叫雞或者招SP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都差不多係咁（除左扑野呢part<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）覺得自由最好玩 要下下顧住對方好煩</blockquote><br />\n拍左幾次拖其實乜都做哂 香港咪又係行街睇戲食飯<br />\n香港咁細 街有行完一日 戲你只會睇一次 好食而你知佢食店亦有限<br />\n頂多比埋你做行山跑步影相唱K啲活動，一年內一定做得哂<br />\n一年後就基本上重複。<br />\n<br />\n你可能話可以去下旅行，當你一年去兩次<br />\n又要近又要識又要好玩，plan死你，我自己去日本玩仲開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd9b80ca49e72afca8085b5b690bc9766fab1e5e","tid":92032,"uid":76945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T10:02:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A5 唔拍了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nA5 多仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc38dd8e26ea8beea92fd1351366af2f8175194","tid":92032,"uid":21322,"like":0,"dis